cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with language and its association with colours. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses crowdsourcing and automatic detection methods to create the lexicon. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with natural language processing and understanding. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of appropriate colours in information visualization and product marketing. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the usefulness of co-occurrence and polarity cues in automatically detecting colour associations.
